<div id="wrapper">
	<%= render 'layouts/navBar'%>

	<div id="content" style="padding-top:50px;">
		
			<h1><span class="eyebrow">Mission Of Hope Haiti</span>
			<br />
			Snap Back</h1>
			<h3>SnapBack: Snap your Photos…then give them back</h3>
<p>
Mission of Hope is always developing new materials to share with our supporters to help them see the Life Transformation happening in Haiti. Chances are if you’re an amateur or even a professional photographer you’ve captured the beauty of Haiti’s people. 
If you have captured some great shots from your recent trip to Haiti please consider sharing them with us for use on our web and print marketing materials. 
Do so by joining our flickr group and uploading your photos!</p>
							<div class="buttonSquareOrange" style="width: 182px; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom:15px; float:left;"><a href="http://www.flickr.com/groups/mohsnapback/" target="_blank">Share your photos &raquo;</a></div>
